	   <tr><td colspan=2>To the person who quoted "People who play Pallys of other races besides D0rfs are the ones who get to 30 and delete their characters", now, I don't know about your server, but on Xegony, the only truly uber pallys are half-elves (like myself) and high-elves. I've seen good Pally humans, and i've beat almost every d0rf pally my level that i've encountered. Don't give d0rfs the upper-hand just because of their base stats. It all comes down to equipment, experience, and your resourcefulness.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
